<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="never-adv">never <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'nevə(r)/    美 /'nevər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>从不；从未；永不：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Never say die</strong>. 
永不言败。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Never put off till tomorrow what you can do today.
今天能做的事绝不要拖到明天。/今日事，今日毕。</p></div>

<p>注: never在句首时，句子要用部分倒装结构，即“Never + 助动词 / 情态动词 / be 动词 + 主语…”。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Never have I heard anything like it! 
我从未听说过这样的事！</p><footer>外研⑦ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I finally got the job I dreamed about. <strong>Never in all my life</strong> had I felt so happy! 
我终于得到了自己梦寐以求的工作，我这辈子从没这么高兴过。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[用于加强语气] 不；没有；不要：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— I told my boss exactly what I thought of her. 
我对老板说了我对她的真实看法。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— You never did. 
你肯定没说过。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>For the safety of yourself and other road users, never drive after consuming alcohol. 
为了你自己和其他行人的安全，切勿酒后驾车。</p><footer>2011 福建</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Never before <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ seen anybody who can play tennis as well as Robert.  （2012 江西）<br />
A.had she<br />
B.she had<br />
C.has she<br />
D.she has  </li>
<li>— How could you be so rude as to walk in here in the middle of my class?
— <strong><em>_</em></strong>_.   （2011 四川）<br />
A.Nothing much.<br />
B.Nothing serious.<br />
C.Never again.<br />
D.Never mind.  </li>
<li>I can <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (永不) be a teacher. I’m not a very patient person.  （2009 湖南改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. C  2. C  3. never  </p></div>